These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, german, mexican
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, emerald, light-blue, fuchsia
1. the person who likes fuchsia is not to the right of the person who likes brown##8
2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the brazilian##1
3. the chinese is on the left or right of the german##3
4. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the person who likes emerald##5
5. the mexican is not to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##8
6. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5
7. the chinese is somewhere between the brazilian and the person who likes emerald##7
8. the chinese and the person who likes fuchsia have the same parity positions##9
9. the german and the person who likes brown have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | brazilian | chinese | german     | mexican |
| Pet           | light-blue   | fuchsia     | emerald | brown  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, rat, horse, turtle
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, sudoku, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is traveling and the owner of the rat have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
6. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
7. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
8. the owner of the turtle is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | turtle     | horse    | rabbit | rat    |
| Hobby      | dancing | drawing | sudoku      | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, japanese, egyptian, argentine
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, avocado, mango, pumpkin
1. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
2. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the egyptian##5
3. the japanese is on the left of the egyptian##1
4. the japanese is on the far left##1
5. the german is on the right of the egyptian##1
6. the egyptian is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
8. the japanese and the person eating avocado have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | japanese    | egyptian   | german    | argentine  |
| Food       | avocado | pumpkin | artichoke | mango |

