.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, spanish, polish, argentine
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, hedgehog, pony
1. the polish is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
2. the owner of the cat and the pakistani have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the dog and the spanish have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
5. the owner of the cat is on the left of the argentine##1
6. the spanish is not the owner of the dog##6
7. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
8. the owner of the cat is on the right of the pakistani##1
9. the owner of the pony is not the argentine##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | pakistani | polish | argentine  | spanish |
| Pet           | dog   | cat     | hedgehog | pony      |

