2. the person eating lime is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
3. the indian is somewhere to the left of the person eating cranberry##5
4. the american and the person eating lime have the same parity positions##9
5. the person eating cranberry and the american have different parity positions##9
6. the indian is not to the left of the person eating pumpkin##8
7. the thai is somewhere to the left of the person eating pumpkin##5
8. the person eating radish is not to the right of the thai##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | radish | pumpkin | lime | cranberry |
| Nationality   | thai        | indian    | american   | brazilian |

