The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, rowing, weightlifting, surfing
1. the chef is somewhere to the right of the entrepreneur##5
2. the person who's sport is rowing and the librarian have the same parity positions##9
3. the chef is the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the librarian is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |  2   |     3     |      4       |
| Job   | entrepreneur | chef | librarian | photographer |
| Pet   | weightlifting         | surfing | rowing    | volleyball   |

