.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, gardening, singing, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, tea, fanta
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking coffee##7
2. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is not the person drinking 7up##6
6. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person drinking fanta have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | gardening | filmmaking | singing |
| Pet     | coffee     | tea     | fanta     | 7up    |

