.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, oliveros, aristoff, prince
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, snowmobile, tram, trike
1. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the chaman-smoker##8
2. the prince-smoker and the person driving the trike have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
5. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the trike##7
6. the prince-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | aristoff | chaman   | oliveros | prince |
| Transport   | tram   | snowmobile | car    | trike      |

