.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-12::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, d&b, indie, rock
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, begonia, bellflower, poppy
1. the fan country is on the right of the fan indie##1
2. the fan indie is not to the left of the person who growspoppy##8
3. the fan rock and the person who growsbegonia have the same parity positions##9
4. the person who growspoppy is the fan rock##1
5. the fan country is somewhere to the right of the person who growszinnia##5
6. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the fan rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |   3   |     4      |
