.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-15::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, peach, potato, tomato
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, skateboard, train, boat
1. the person eating peach and the person driving the boat have the same parity positions##9
2. the person driving the boat is not to the left of the person eating peach##8
3. the person eating mango is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the person driving the boat##7
4. the person driving the boat is somewhere between the person driving the train and the person eating mango##7
5. the person driving the skateboard is not the person eating tomato##6
6. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating mango##1
7. the person eating potato is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | tomato | mango | peach | potato  |
| Music-Genre   | bike    | skateboard | boat | train |

