2. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
4. the person traveling to paris is in an odd position##4
5. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
6. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
8. the person traveling to colone and the person drinking almond-milk have the same parity positions##9
9. the person traveling to san-francisco and the person drinking sprite have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea   | fanta  | sprite  | almond-milk |
| Movie-Genre   | paris | san-francisco | hannover | colone      |

