2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person traveling to miami is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
4. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the right of the person traveling to london##8
5. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the hedgehog and the person traveling to boston have the same parity positions##9
7. the owner of the cat and the person traveling to miami have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
| Job   | boston | marseilles | london | miami |
| Pet   | hedgehog    | fish   | rat        | cat            |

