3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who growsiris and the person who's hobby is skydiving have the same parity positions##9
5. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | balloon-flower    | iris | azalea | lily |
| Hobby      | puzzles | skydiving   | board-games   | baking   |

